{"tid":307950,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"［jj插沙］鏡頭變成咁，點整好？","createTime":"2017-07-03T17:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T17:43:14.000Z","uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f28c28038099db4577dc418213fce78abefa1990","tid":307950,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"小弟係英國<br />\n今日影相時，成部相機連腳架跌左落地<br />\n結果發現個鏡凹左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己整唔整得返？<br />\n開機時個鏡頭zoom唔到出黎<br />\n仲吱吱聲<br />\n畫面黑晒，寫住鏡頭錯誤，將自動熄機<br />\n部機對我好重要架 雖然好舊<br />\n向各位巴絲求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬分感激<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/014725_08cb69dda5ae9f4eaeb66244bd8e9dff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F014725_08cb69dda5ae9f4eaeb66244bd8e9dff.jpg&h=d64a0c15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42b37e647a97f2bb3a2e447aeca0d47c3b40dc2e","tid":307950,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"拎去保養。"},{"pid":"a86d7d6a8c64e56f85ec43b6d7002b0ecfafb1db","tid":307950,"uid":51056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T20:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎去保養。</blockquote><br />\n5年前買架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f7e7b2b13f63d21d83c93096a0d876472cf066","tid":307950,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T21:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎去保養。</blockquote><br />\n5年前買架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsx50?<br />\n換過部細少少既sx730啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13080627215ddac4b67efc467be65ed42b635fe","tid":307950,"uid":70183,"like":0,"di